    "description": "<p>A torrent of wind erupts from your hand in a direction you choose. Each creature that starts its turn in the area or moves into the area must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pushed 15 feet from you in the direction of the line.</p><p>Any creature in the area must spend 2 feet of movement for every foot moved when trying to approach you.</p><p>The blast of wind extinguishes small fires and disperses gas or vapor.</p><p>You can use a bonus action to change the direction of the gust.</p>",
